{"tid":896302,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"好評如潮？！DC 年度大作《Aquaman》首波評價搶先出爐","createTime":"2018-11-10T01:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T04:09:26.000Z","uid":52215,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d64affbacbe46116ba72a589241549215b8cd4","tid":896302,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"DC Comics 最新超級英雄大作《Aquaman》在 10 月初迎來第 2 波官方預告後，昨日則釋出最新電影角色海報。而近日國外則進行了首次試片電影會，究竟《Aquaman》在華裔大導 James Wan 溫子仁的操刀下，能否成功翻轉大眾對 DC 電影的印象呢？根據多方 Twitter 評論指出，目前《Aquaman》多為正面評價，包括稱讚亞特蘭提斯王國的塑造令人印象深刻，Black Manta 與 Mera 等人的優異表現，甚至有網民將《Aquaman》作為個人 DC 電影排行榜第一位。<br />\n<br />\n此外也談到 DC 新總監 Walter Hamada 在更名「Worlds of DC」後，成功改變了 DC 的電影方向，並稱讚  James Wan 的傑出指導，但也有人指出《Aquaman》並不到完美，但絕對能讓影迷感到娛樂性十足。"},{"pid":"e16544b5b68df682744f2e8c0fa44ae3e3894a09","tid":896302,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"有神奇女俠既水準已經好滿足"},{"pid":"1fe17b7279b4eed37ddca188a2287a01d106c60c","tid":896302,"uid":55533,"like":56,"dislike":4,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"e16544b5b68df682744f2e8c0fa44ae3e3894a09","tid":896302,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"有神奇女俠既水準已經好滿足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"因為gal gadot姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換做captain marvel個阿嬸做實屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.comicbook.com/2017/06/wonder-woman-glasses-1000325-1280x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.comicbook.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fwonder-woman-glasses-1000325-1280x0.jpg&h=bd9210d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"124e5aa48f0f155173d67bafa6e4b1636dce97c0","tid":896302,"uid":157304,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"rep